               <code code="51945-4" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="PACKAGE LABEL.PRINCIPAL DISPLAY PANEL"/>
               <title>OXYGEN COMPRESSED LABEL</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>OXYGEN COMPRESSED U.S.P.  UN 1072 - OXYGEN - 2 - WARNING: SECURE ALL CYLINDERS WHILE IN STORAGE AND IN USE.  USE IN ACCORDANCE WITH MATERIAL SAFETY DATA SHEET AND SAFETY PRECAUTIONS RECOMMENDED BY THE SUPPLIER.  DO NOT REMOVE THIS PRODUCT LABEL.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <renderMultiMedia referencedObject="HOLOX1"/>
                  </paragraph>
               </text>
